{"tid":339481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：中國口岸區不可設特別條款保障港人","createTime":"2017-07-29T06:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T03:37:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71147b1bd17fbc398fb5db796189e6f80bf1d6b3","tid":339481,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】運輸及房屋局局長陳帆說，不能夠要求內地當局在一地兩檢內地口岸區加入條款特別保障港人，但會向內地當局反映港人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆又指，一地兩檢設在福田或深圳北並不可行，因為高鐵香港段由港人出資，以西九龍作總站才可發揮最大效益，預計可為港人提供一萬個有關飲食及零售等相關職位。"},{"pid":"018cab945f09de0439674ced47c9e06e071a226a","tid":339481,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=230183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230183&d=Khx3AQKzWih%2FwQaBBRTJcf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5561406e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230183&h=c936d26c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=230183</a>"},{"pid":"5383f672be6c80932c40ca7d0a5949a649451ceb","tid":339481,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32af24fbd1cd71fd7680f68023253569b4c351e2","tid":339481,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"呢條友上任冇幾耐就已經咁多sound bite<br />\n睇好佢繼承唔得掂"},{"pid":"6eaffcb280b6194dd9ad70bdf396bf99a83da515","tid":339481,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣一萬個職位</blockquote><br />\n加埋一個唔知會唔會因高有增加遊客的數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67eb40158d87fcdbc5ecf8a46dad4a00becbc07","tid":339481,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣一萬個職位</blockquo